{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_52_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 今晩はあともう一つだけ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……こんなに飲んだのはいつぶりかしら\nでも、夜はまだこれからよ。私についてこれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… I wonder when was the last time I drank this much.\nBut the night is still young. Can you keep up with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6569592975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "カッコ良く言っていますけどさっきからずっと酒を\n飲んでるだけですよ。その一杯で終わりにしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're trying to sound cool‚ but you've just been drinking\nall this time. Let's make that your last drink.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は特別……とはいえ莉央さん、少し飲み過ぎだ）\n（もう少し前に止めておけば良かったな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today is special… but even so‚ Rio-san is drinking a bit too much.）\n（I should have stopped her a bit earlier.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "嫌よ、まだ貴方との夜は終わらないわ！　あら、いつの\n間にか貴方のグラスが空いてるわね。おかわりを――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way‚ my night with you isn't over yet!\nOh‚ your glass is empty already? Can I have a refill――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、その前に、ビーチに出てみませんか？\n莉央さんにしてほしいことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-before that‚ why don't we go out to the beach?\nThere's something I'd like you to do‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "してほしいこと？　もう外は真っ暗だけど……何かしら\nいいわよ、連れて行ってちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something you'd like me to do? It's already pitch dark outside… what could it be?\nFine‚ take me there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 52.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 52.9
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 53.6333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 53.6333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "んー、空気が美味しい……。夜のビーチもいいわね\nあら？　こんな所にもテーブルがあるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ the air is refreshing… A night beach is nice too.\nOh? There's even a table here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33766.66793819999,
          "startTime": 88.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……夜の砂浜の、オープンテラス席？\n洒落てるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… an open terrace seat on the night beach?\nHow stylish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 72.4999987285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "このお店の名物なんですよ\n良かったらここで一休みしませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's this shop's specialty.\nWould you like to take a break here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ。座りましょう\n……にぎやかな店内と違って、ここは静かね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine. Let's sit down.\n…It's much quieter here than inside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 84.2333320618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "聞こえるのは波の音だけ\nまるで、この世界に私達二人しかいないみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All I can hear is the sound of waves.\nIt's like there are only the two of us in this world.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 91.8666653951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達と、砂浜と波しかないわ。ふふっ……こんな風に\n何もない時間もいいわね。心が落ち着くわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just us‚ the beach‚ and the waves. Fufu…\nquiet moments like this are nice too. It calms my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "貴方がしてほしいことって、これだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this what you wanted me to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.300007375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 106.3333407084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "はい。いつも多忙で気を張っている莉央さんだから\n何もしない時間を、過ごしてほしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Since Rio-san is always busy and on edge‚\nI wanted you to spend time doing nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのね……。あら？　楽器の音が聞こえるわ\nこれは……三線？　沖縄の伝統楽器よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Oh? I can hear the sound of an instrument.\nThis is… a sanshin? An Okinawan traditional instrument‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8000025431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 119.8000025431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。この店のもう一つの名物が\n三線の店内ライブなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Another specialty of this shop\nis live sanshin performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2000025431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 131.500007375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "素敵なBGMも用意されてるなんて気が利いてる\nじゃない。いつまでだって、ここにいられそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's so thoughtful of them to have lovely BGM.\nI could stay here forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7558404242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "……素敵なプレゼントをありがとう\nねぇ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you for the wonderful present.\nHey‚ {user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8000167846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 144.0333661396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "今晩はあともう一つだけ\n私のお願いを聞いてほしいの……いいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have just one more request\nfor you tonight… would that be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.0333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、マネージャーとして出来ることなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes‚ if it's something I can do as a manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.766699473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 157.3000328063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……ぷっ、そういうところ、貴方らしいわね\n私のお願いはね……おかわりのドリンクがほしいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hah‚ that's so like you.\nMy request is… I'd like another drink.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 164.1666966755
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "今度は泡盛カクテルを飲みたいんだけど……\nメニューを見て、ずっと気になってたの。いいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time I want to drink an awamori cocktail…\nI’ve been curious about it since I saw it on the menu… is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.8000300089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 173.7333722431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　なんだ、そんなことですか。いつもと\n少し雰囲気が違ったのでもっと難しいお願いかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Is that all? You seemed different than usual‚\nso I thought it might be a more difficult request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.9333633422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 182.4667055765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこととは何よ。今日はもうだいぶ飲んでるでしょ\n飲み過ぎだって思ってない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean \"is that all\"? I've already drunk quite a bit today‚ haven't I?\nDon't you think I'm drinking too much?",
